headline: KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY) Stock Slips 11% Amid Market Volatility
summary: Last week, KeyCorp (NYSE:KEY) experienced a 11% decline in its share price. This price movement unfolded against the backdrop of broader market volatility, where stocks slipped as investors absorbed tariff developments and escalating economic concerns including talk from former President Trump on tariffs impacting sectors that KeyCorp operates in. The Dow Jones and S&P 500 experienced declines of 1.2% and 0.8% respectively, and the overall market fell by 4.6%. This downward pressure impacted...
